      This list is not exhaustive. The absence of a specific title does not imply any different relationship with its owner.
    </p>

    <h2>Fan content and community guidelines</h2>
    <p>
      Where publisher fan content policies, community use policies, or similar licences exist, content on this site is intended to comply with them. If you are a rights holder and believe any content here infringes your intellectual property, please contact <a href="mailto:matt@hobbinomicon.com">matt@hobbinomicon.com</a> and it will be reviewed promptly.
